Termitron/Nightlight::

Termitron decided that The Queen would rest better in a quarter. He 
opened the cr's door. Nightlight was incounceos (Is that the 
spelling?)for cr. Her wounds had heal, but she wouldn't wake up in a 
large while. Termitron picked her up and  left cr's chambers and he 
walked with the femme in arm towards quarters section where he found 
a quarter that he belived would be abbeter place for his Queen.

He reached a quarter, it was a perfect place that the Royalty rest. 
he left her in the bed and walked out side the room. He would be out 
side, his Queen would be safe.
